title: Frankie & Fern's: Brunch, Coffee, and Dinner Spot
blurb: Brunch and coffee daily, dinner Fri-Sun, plus last Mondays.
description: Frankie & Fern's offers a delightful dining experience with brunch and coffee available every day. Dinner service is available from Friday to Sunday, providing a perfect setting for family meals. Additionally, they are open every last Monday of the month for dinner, making it a unique spot for a monthly treat. The restaurant aims to create a welcoming atmosphere for families and individuals alike, with a focus on quality food and friendly service. Enjoy a relaxed meal in a cozy environment, perfect for a casual outing or a special occasion.

title: Frankie & Fern's @ Holland Village - Playground
blurb: Indoor playground at Holland Village for families.
description: Frankie & Fern's is an indoor playground located at Holland Village. It offers a safe and fun environment for children to play and explore. The playground features various play areas designed to stimulate creativity and physical activity. It is accessible via public transport and car, with detailed directions provided for both. The venue aims to provide a convenient and enjoyable experience for families visiting with their children. The playground is located on level 4 and is accessible by elevator. Frankie & Fern's is a great place for kids to have fun and parents to relax.
